name: Toto Cookie Blast
description:
Toto Cookie Blast is a cute game with classic jellies, cakes, candies and cool blasting unlike other fast-paced cake blast game. You plan your every pop to get the level target. It's very challenging for your.
Features:
- Two game modes: cookie cake classic and arcade...
- Fresh and cute items.Various of kinds for tasting, enjoying.
- Amazing cake jam blasting, jelly splash effects.
- Easy to play, hard to master in cookie mania. It’s a good way to practice your brain and
